  "text": "The first approach for reconstructing provenance we devised was inspired by AI planning techniques and change detection algorithms, as described in [CITATION_1] . The goal of this work was to reconstruct the sequence of transformations between entities by using the A* algorithm combined with a heuristic function based on the edit distance. In this case, there are three limitations :",
